# On-Train Food Ordering & Feedback System — Implementation Plan

A full-stack Next.js application that solves food quality & delivery timing unpredictability for train passengers. The system uses a mock NTES API for live train tracking, triggers food preparation dynamically based on GPS distance to the destination station, shows a live map with the delivery agent, and releases escrow funds only after OTP confirmation.

## Proposed Changes

